---
title: Sun-Dried Tomato & Cuke Sandwiches with Red Pepper Hummus & Feta
description: Fresh, crunchy, filling, tasty: What more could you ask for in a sandwich? Ok, sure, vegetarian? Check. Quick? Check check. This sourdough sando’s got layers of creamy red pepper hummus studded with tangy, salty feta, meaty sun-dried tomatoes, sliced crisp cukes, and greens dressed in a shallot vinaigrette (with plenty leftover for a side salad)—all in 10 minutes. Win!
